name: Booster
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Booster (BOO) hopes to solve a series of problems in the current DeFi ecosystem and hopes that users' assets can be increased in a more convenient way. Booster will become a one-stop service platform, where users can complete a series of DeFi actions such as deposits, borrowing, and leveraged mining.
